===============================================
|ID|OPERATOR                         |NAME    |
-----------------------------------------------
|0 |PX COORDINATOR                   |        |
|1 |└─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR             |:EX10001|
|2 |  └─HASH JOIN                    |        |
|3 |    ├─EXCHANGE IN DISTR          |        |
|4 |    │ └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (PKEY)|:EX10000|
|5 |    │   └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR      |        |
|6 |    │     └─TABLE FULL SCAN      |t1      |
|7 |    └─SUBPLAN SCAN               |v3      |
|8 |      └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR    |        |
|9 |        └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |t2      |
===============================================
